[SN]TITLE[SN]
Withybush Hospital ward closed to contain infection

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A ward at Withybush Hospital has been temporary closed to visitors and new admissions due to an outbreak of a bug.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Several patients on ward one have experienced diarrhoea and vomiting and specialists have been called in to reduce the spread of infection.
Hywel Dda University Health Board has reassured patients the hospital remains open, with operations continuing as normal.
Patients will be contacted about any changes, the health board added.
